data.description: Enjoy your Very Spacious 2Bedrooms/2Baths Pool Home Situated on a Quiet no outlet county street just blocks from Daytona Beach city line. This Charming Open, Split Floor Plan with Vaulted Ceilings & Skylights providing Natural Lighting to both Bathrooms and Kitchen.  Both Master Bedroom & Large Family Room leads into a large screened in lanai & pool.  Bring your fur babies too as the backyard is fenced in with 2 Gates & Room for your Boat/RV on the side yard.  Also, a Shed for extra storage and a 2 car garage with a pull down ladder to attic.  So Many Upgrades: Recently installed Solar System (Ask for Details), Newer Kitchen counter tops, New Well Pump, Water Softening System Installed & more!  Hurry, this one will go FAST!  All information intended to be accurate, but not guaranteed.
